    "texte_orig": "The day of prophecy draws nigh...\nPrepare yourself, cursed whelp of Loki!\nQuetzalcoatl\nLiar, deceiver, stealer of my\nthrone! I will have my revenge!\nDon't make me laugh... Have you already\nforgotten how you knocked me from the sky?\nQuetzalcoatl\nUrgh... Still, I cannot forgive thee!\nPrepare thyself!\nAmeretat\nI have found you, tempting humans\ninto violence... I did not imagine you\nwould take the guise of a woman.\nAmeretat\nBy Spenta Mainyu's order, I will destroy you!",
